  <h2>
    <span class="">在哪儿借这本书</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;

  </h2>


  <ul class="bs more-after">
      
      <li style="border: none">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/link2/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bplisn.net.cn%2FBookSearch.aspx%3FISBN%3D978-7-101-05418-7&amp;subject=7101054188&amp;type=borrow&amp;library=10007&amp;link2key=c5fb1023a8" target="_blank">北京市公共图书馆(1)</a>
